description:
Save time, money & extend your battery life by resizing your photos before sending them to your friends and family. 

This app resizes and compresses your pictures without losing quality. 

Key features:

 + single AND batch image conversion (resize any number of photos with just one tap;

 +  3 size options (small, medium and large);

 + no internet connection required - all photos are processed locally; 

 + fast and very easy to use;

 + works with webOS 1.4.5 and higher and is webOS 2 ready;

 + resolutions: 1024x768, 800x600, 640x480 - your original photos are unchanged - new, resized copies are saved in your Photos-Download folder;
